{"tid":2195360,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【中印衝突】網傳兩軍「打爛仔交」 解放軍追踢印軍屁股 隔岸觀戰兵忍唔住笑","createTime":"2020-09-09T06:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T06:42:22.000Z","uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51f3750af5526972ebb4f44d8b4bd73cd7229647","tid":2195360,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"中印邊境衝突再度升溫，兩國軍隊自前日爆發45年來首次開火事件後，又在拉達克（Ladakh）河谷發生肢體衝突。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n有印民網民就形容，兩國21世紀「戰爭」，竟淪為史前野蠻人的對戰。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n印度《經濟時報》（The Economic Times）則指，從影片中可見，解放方至少派出40名士兵，在邊境與印度軍對峙，每位士兵更配有木棍、魚叉，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n．．．．．．．，有人更拿手中武器擊打已倒地的印軍。<br />\n解放軍追擊後退的印軍，。。。。。。。<br />\n，還有人拿起木棍等武器揮棒亂舞，雙方還互扯紅布條警告標語，更有印軍後退不慎倒地，遭解放軍用手中武器擊打。不過，在對岸拍攝、。。。。。看到這般畫面時卻忍不住笑了出來，影像中也收錄了拍攝者的笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n有印度網民則嘲諷，該段影片，讓他感到21世紀戰爭也可能像史前野蠻人般用腳踏或揮舞刀劍來對陣。．．．．．．．．．．。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/ 印度《經濟時報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200909/TGJL5FGJHFHP5NS7NAZIHU6CUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200909%2FTGJL5FGJHFHP5NS7NAZIHU6CUY%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=461769d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200909%2FTGJL5FGJHFHP5NS7NAZIHU6CUY%2F&h=8d5a6331\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200909/TGJL5FGJHFHP5NS7NAZIHU6CUY/</a>"},{"pid":"22ac1dc3abfc20f5429f74088c9076e904d98acc","tid":2195360,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:36:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾人口大國係咁上下架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d463c84f109e9c83ef15af799a3bf05f40cd52d","tid":2195360,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"強国人係咪唔知上次佢哋慘敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8a8550e3fc646144f7677de66129e54f69b0e8","tid":2195360,"uid":215249,"like":0,"d